description:
Ben Falcone [Tammy, Superintelligence, The Boss, What To Expect When You’re Expecting, Enough Said, Bridesmaids] talks with Anna about his new superhero movie Thunder Force, working with Melissa McCarthy (his wife), casting his friends, what it takes to be funny, comic books, The Ding Dang Gang, missing his answering machine, how to propose marriage while waiting for the plumber to finish installing a new toilet, and more. Later in the episode, dating coach, matchmaker, and founder of Level Connections, April Beyer joins Anna to offer some perspective and advice to a listener in need.

Learn more about April and LEVEL by visiting  www.levelconnections.com
